signature_matches.name: contain an embedded PE file
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: contain an embedded PE file
    namespace: executable/subfile/pe
    authors:
      - moritz.raabe@mandiant.com
    scopes:
      static: file
      dynamic: file
    mbc:
      - Execution::Install Additional Program [B0023]
    examples:
      - Practical Malware Analysis Lab 01-04.exe_:0x4060
  features:
    - or:
      - count(characteristic(embedded pe)): 1 or more
      - count(string(This program cannot be run in DOS mode.)): 2 or more

signature_matches.name: packed with Neolite
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: packed with Neolite
    namespace: anti-analysis/packer/neolite
    authors:
      - william.ballenthin@mandiant.com
    scopes:
      static: file
      dynamic: file
    att&ck:
      - Defense Evasion::Obfuscated Files or Information::Software Packing [T1027.002]
    mbc:
      - Anti-Static Analysis::Software Packing [F0001]
    references:
      - https://www.hexacorn.com/blog/2016/12/15/pe-section-names-re-visited/
  features:
    - or:
      - section: .neolite
      - section: .neolit

signature_matches.name: compiled from Visual Basic
signature_matches.rule_src:
rule:
  meta:
    name: compiled from Visual Basic
    namespace: compiler/vb
    authors:
      - "@williballenthin"
    scopes:
      static: file
      dynamic: file
    examples:
      - 9bca6b99e7981208af4c7925b96fb9cf
  features:
    - and:
      - string: /VB5!.*/
      - import: msvbvm60.ThunRTMain
